# WaveCommerce AI Configuration - Simple Setup

# Pexels API for image generation
VITE_PEXELS_API_KEY=your_pexels_api_key_here

# Printify API for automated product creation (Printify handles Shopify automatically)
VITE_PRINTIFY_API_TOKEN=your_printify_api_token_here
VITE_PRINTIFY_SHOP_ID=your_printify_shop_id_here

# Setup Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env (remove .example)
# 2. Get Pexels API key: pexels.com/api (free signup)
# 3. Get Printify API token: printify.com → Account → API → Generate Token
# 4. Get Printify Shop ID: printify.com → My Stores → (click your Shopify store, ID is in the URL)
# 5. Restart dev server: npm run dev

# That's it! Printify automatically publishes products to your connected Shopify store.
# No Shopify API credentials needed.